      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/Palacio_de_Gobierno_de_Xalapa_1.JPG/1280px-Palacio_de_Gobierno_de_Xalapa_1.JPG" alt="Xalapa Picture" class="w-64" />
      <div class="w-full">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h1 class="text-3xl">Xalapa Tour</h1>
          <p class="text-lg">Discover awesome places on Xalapa.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-neutral-200 flex justify-between">
          <div class="grow">
            <p class="text-sm">Around 42+ reviews here from visitors.</p>
            <p class="text-lg">$500 USD per person</p>
          </div>
          <button class="rounded bg-teal-500 text-white text-md w-fit grow">Visit</button>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-xs">Image taken from Wikimedia</p>
</Preview>

But what if we let other weight tricks join the party?

<Preview>
  <div class="shadow rounded flex">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/Palacio_de_Gobierno_de_Xalapa_1.JPG/1280px-Palacio_de_Gobierno_de_Xalapa_1.JPG" alt="Xalapa Picture" class="w-64" />
      <div class="w-full">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-black">Xalapa Tour</h1>
          <p class="text-lg font-light">Discover awesome places on Xalapa.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-neutral-200 flex justify-between">
          <div class="grow">
            <p class="text-sm font-light text-neutral-500">Around 42+ reviews here from visitors.</p>
            <p class="text-md"><span class="font-bold text-lg">$500 USD</span> per person</p>
          </div>
          <button class="rounded bg-teal-500 text-white text-md w-fit grow">Visit</button>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600">Image taken from Wikimedia</p>
</Preview>

The price is bold now. The reviews are lighter. The headline is black. The button is ready. Font size did some work, but weight and color did the heavy lifting.

## No Diet Required for Weight Loss

- Weight is your volume control for attention.
- Use size, color, font weight, and fill together.
- If everything is heavy, nothing is. (Sorry, gymbros.)
- Font size never works alone. You need the whole team.
